{"about_the_game":"<strong>Seconds Till Destruction</strong> is a violent top-down shooter with heavy randomization and an emphasis on fast reaction times.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE WAR AGAINST HUMANITY</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008800/extras/seconds_steam_1_alt.gif?t=1731038922\" /><br>Humanity has nearly won the war against the machines. In an act of desperation, the remaining robots are sent back in time to locate and kill humanity's future leaders.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HEAVY RANDOMIZATION</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008800/extras/seconds_steam_4_alt.gif?t=1731038922\" /><br>Every run is an endless gauntlet of random rooms with randomized enemy spawns and random weapons to use. Adaptability is key.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TIME'S TICKING</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008800/extras/seconds_steam_2.gif?t=1731038922\" /><br>Your time machine is highly unstable and self-destructs after six seconds. Use that precious time to come up with a strategy for each room, or improvise and go guns blazing.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WEAPONS AND MUTATIONS</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008800/extras/seconds_steam_3_alt.gif?t=1731038922\" /><br>Unlock a variety of weapons to use in your runs, ranging from the plain Auto Shotgun to the deadly Sawblade Launcher. Use Mutators to spice up the gameplay further with various effects.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GO FOR THE GOLD</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008800/extras/seconds_steam_5.gif?t=1731038922\" /><br>Clear as many rooms as you can for bragging rights and glory. Chase high scores by killing enemies as fast and efficiently as possible.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asse